%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Wrong pattern will return unevaluated expression:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
absoluteValue[-I]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
absoluteValue[-I]

