%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Clear the assigned variables:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
ClearAll[x,y]

